{"tid":723362,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】李嘉欣48歲生日 老公許晉亨熊抱晒恩愛","createTime":"2018-06-30T10:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T11:48:42.000Z","uid":48905,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d26862542224c9728cb26dc2f78a413407753ae9","tid":723362,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"剛剛度過48歲生日嘅李嘉欣（Michele），今日喺Instagram上載咗三張相，其中一張係佢老公許晉亨從後熊抱攬實佢，兩公婆四手交纏，好鬼sweet，Michele仲留言寫住︰「About pre-summer gathering Thank you ladies」<br />\n<br />\n雖然係迎接夏天嘅聚會，但其中一張相，只有Michele同面前個好靚嘅花花蛋糕，估計Michele呢班girl friend幫佢補祝生日，當中有李民橋老婆Bonnie（鄺淑孄）、邱達昌嘅大女邱詠賢Winnie（邱詠筠）、二女Wendy（邱詠賢）兩姐妹等，而同場仲有佢老公許晉亨出現。<br />\n其實李嘉欣喺今個月20日生日，正日嗰日佢就冇post相，而生日前夕就有post過同家姐李嘉明，同埋啲girl friend慶祝生日嘅相，之前就未見有老公份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/182716_e04a60ea3b0fe52d24a71fa9133cccd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F182716_e04a60ea3b0fe52d24a71fa9133cccd5.jpg&h=6e1f6a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">李嘉欣同一班好姊妹，包括Bonnie（後排左一）、Wendy（前排左一）、winnie（前排右一）等。(ig圖片)</span>"},{"pid":"6b59101d27552e37a0e65b1fca0bfd37d675dab9","tid":723362,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"冇頭條廣告"},{"pid":"4f1363d107296ba7ce069481da7535333800ff89","tid":723362,"uid":15730,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T19:02:23.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你呀！<br />\n張相做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9dac4c102248e208be034058531cf689718eca","tid":723362,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"張相兩個好似有仇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c436a84305719bf4196cf3baa9393423b7